
Set folder detials like: https://www.cloudways.com/blog/configure-virtual-host-on-windows-10-for-wordpress/

install ngrok tunnel: 
follow installing and runnnng documentation from here: https://dashboard.ngrok.com/tunnels/agents

for setting host header 
ngrok http 80 --host-header="mylocalapp.test"

OR 
ngrok http --host-header=mylocalapp.test 80


For ngrok existing task killing: use this command: taskkill /f /im ngrok.exe
